  "title": "DELIVERY ASSISTANT",
  "description": "<p><strong>Roles &\nResponsibilities</strong></p><p><strong>Job\nDuties</strong>\n</p><ul><li>Assist with loading and unloading of fragile goods onto the vehicle and ensuring safe\ndelivery to customers.</li><li>Assist in warehousing and order packing.</li><li>Able to work flexible and long hours</li><li>Willing to work OT</li><li>Physically fit, self-discipline, responsible, punctual, reliable</li><li>CPF Contributions</li></ul><p><strong>Job\nRequirements:</strong>                \n</p><ul><li>Basic proficiency English/Tamil</li><li>Basic organizational skills for handling orders, paperwork, and delivery schedules. </li><li>Physically fit and able to lift loads up to 25kg</li></ul><p><strong>Package:</strong>              \n5.5-day work week (Mon-Fri 9.00am: 6.00pm, Sat 9.00am to 1:00pm)\n$1700- $2000 (Depending on experience)<br /></p>",
